ence\": \"Defending champion US qualified for the last eight on Wednesday, July 31, and go through as Group A winners.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two from each group advance to the quarters and the best two third-placed teams go through on points difference.\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Greece's victory, which keeps them in the mix for a quarter-final spot came courtesy of Milwaukee Bucks forward Giannis Antetokounmpo, who was his usual prolific self, scoring 20 points to go with 7 rebounds and 6 assists.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2765, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.392612317996499e-15, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2853, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee_Bucks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.16315549695959e-40, \"text\": \"Milwaukee Bucks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee_Bucks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee_Bucks\"}, {\"begin\": 2877, \"end\": 2898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giannis Antetokounmpo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 'Greek Freak' was helped by Dinos Mitoglou and Thomas Walkup, who finished with a combined 31 points.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3021, \"end\": 3035